ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectPayments Received under the Atlantic Groundfish Licence Retirement Program Remission Order
PrecisPAYMENTS RECEIVED UNDER THE ATLANTIC GROUNDFISH LICENCE RETIREMENT PROGRAM REMISSION ORDER in order to remit a portion of the federal income tax, late filing penalties, employment insurance benefit repayments, and interest paid or payable thereon in respect of the 1998, 1999, 2000, 2001 or 2002 tax year, as the case may be, by fishers who received payments under the Atlantic Groundfish Licence Retirement Program.
